  public static final String PRIVACY_CONTENT9 = "TravelFront, a company incorporated in the Cayman Islands (hereinafter referred to as “Travala”, “we” or “us”) recognises the importance of privacy. In this privacy policy, we describe how we collect, use, and disclose information that we obtain about visitors to our website, www.travala.com, and the services available through our website.";
